<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb60c3fa7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300a–6"><num value="300a–6">§ 300a–6.</num><heading> Prohibition against funding programs using abortion as family planning method</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">None of the funds appropriated under this subchapter shall be used in programs where abortion is a method of family planning.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb60c3fa8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373">July 1, 1944, ch. 373</ref>, title X, § 1008, as added <ref href="/us/pl/91/572/s6/c">Pub. L. 91–572, § 6(c)</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1508">84 Stat. 1508</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
